# Comets Studio

## What It Is
AI-powered component and full-app builder. Local-first (Ollama), multi-provider (DeepSeek, Kimi, etc.), with project templates, live preview, Vercel deploy, and ZIP export.

## Key Paths
- `lib/ai-service.ts` – AI providers
- `lib/stores/chat-store.ts` – chat state, projectFiles
- `lib/project-templates.ts` – full project starters
- `lib/vercel-deploy.ts` – deploy + export
- `components/code-playground/CodePlayground.tsx` – Sandpack + FileTree
- `components/chat/chat-interface.tsx` – main UI

## Design System
- Slate/gray palette, no glassmorphism
- Lucide icons, Tailwind, accessible (ARIA)

## APIs
- `POST /api/chat` – streaming chat
- `POST /api/explain` – code explanation
- `POST /api/deploy` – Vercel deploy
- `POST /api/export` – ZIP export
